Section 1(Group Rules Act 10th January,2022)

A)If you follow me:-
i)Stay in this group.
ii)Respect each and every member of the group.
iii)Ask your programming related doubts in the group.
iv)Give answer if you know as soon as you see that someone asks a question in the group as this is a "Helping Group".

B)Don't change group name
C)Don't add or remove people(All those who are currently in this group are my followers)

Section 2(Language Act 10th January,2022)

There are thousands of languages used in the world.But in this group we would use only 2 languages.
A)English
B)Hindi
